Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, è Watanuki. Yoshikazu Watanuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.00,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs25\fnTimes New Roman\b1\pos(440.752,41.525)\c&H131F1E&}Yoshikazu Watanuki
