Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.10,0:24:27.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Nel prossimo episodio di Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.38,0:24:30.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Il caso misterioso \Ndella talpa aliena, seconda parte".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.33,0:24:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prossimo indizio per Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.19,0:24:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tombino.
