Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.79,0:24:53.93,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Che buco starà scavando\N l'agente Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:55.17,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,La sua tomba!
